      </div>

      {!fugleKey && (
        <div className="text-yellow-500 text-sm mb-4 bg-yellow-900/20 p-2 rounded border border-yellow-700">
          ⚠️ 尚未設定 Fugle API Key，分析時將無法取得精確即時股價。建議前往設定頁面填寫。
        </div>
      )}

      {error && (
        <div className="p-4 bg-red-900/30 border border-red-500 text-red-200 rounded-lg mb-6">
          {error}
        </div>
      )}

      {result && (
        <div className="animate-fade-in space-y-6">
          {/* Header Card */}
          <div className="bg-cardBg rounded-xl p-6 shadow-xl border-l-4 border-twRed">
            <div className="flex justify-between items-start">
              <div>
                <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">{result.name} <span className="text-gray-400 text-xl">({result.symbol})</span></h2>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span className={`px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm font-bold ${
                    result.trend === 'BULLISH' ? 'bg-twRed/20 text-twRed' : 
                    result.trend === 'BEARISH' ? 'bg-twGreen/20 text-twGreen' : 'bg-gray-700 text-gray-300'
                  }`}>
                    {result.trend === 'BULLISH' ? '看漲 (Bullish)' : result.trend === 'BEARISH' ? '看跌 (Bearish)' : '盤整 (Neutral)'}
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div className="text-right">
                <p className="text-gray-400 text-sm">預測區間</p>
                <p className="text-2xl font-mono font-bold">
                  <span className="text-twGreen">{result.predictedLow}</span> - <span className="text-twRed">{result.predictedHigh}</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <StockChart 
              currentPrice={(result.predictedHigh + result.predictedLow) / 2} // Fallback visualization
              predictedHigh={result.predictedHigh}
              predictedLow={result.predictedLow}
              buyPoint={result.buyPoint}
              sellPoint={result.sellPoint}
            />
          </div>

          {/* Analysis Details */}
          <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div className="bg-cardBg rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
              <h3 className="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">策略建議</h3>
              <div className="space-y-4">
                <div className="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <span className="text-gray-400">建議買入點 (Buy)</span>
                  <span className="text-xl font-bold text-twRed">{result.buyPoint}</span>
                </div>
                <div className="flex justify-between items-center">
